            <note xml:id="foot.f2">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4021.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from John Scott, 3 March 1863</ref>. <ref target="../nameregs/nameregs_1957.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">Asa Gray</ref> gave this information in a missing postscript to his <ref target="./DCP-LETT-3799.xml" resp="#automat" cert="low">letter to CD of 10 November 1862</ref> (<ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 10). See <ref target="../bibliographies/bibl_1581.xml" resp="#mjhawkins"><hi rend="italic">Correspondence</hi></ref> vol. 10, <ref target="./DCP-LETT-3830.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter to Asa Gray, 26[–7] November [1862]</ref> and n. 3.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f3">See enclosure.</note>
            <note xml:id="foot.f4">See <ref target="./DCP-LETT-4021.xml" resp="#mjhawkins">letter from John Scott, 3 March 1863</ref>.</note>
